{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "mentorconnect-final-cookie-auth",
    "name": "MentorConnect – Complete API Test Suite (HttpOnly Cookie + Fixed Auth)",
    "description": "Final Postman collection for **all 21 endpoints** with:\n\n- HttpOnly `jwt` cookie auth (no Bearer token)\n- Fixed `authorize` middleware\n- File upload via `form-data`\n- Auto ID extraction\n- Full validation + error tests\n- Admin flow included\n\n**How to use:**\n1. Import → Set `base_url`\n2. Run `Signup` or `Login` → cookie set\n3. All protected routes work automatically\n\n**No Authorization headers needed**",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST /api/auth/signup",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Signup successful\", function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.success).to.be.true;",
                  "    pm.environment.set('user_id', json.user.id);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"HttpOnly jwt cookie is set\", function () {",
                  "    const cookies = pm.cookies.jar().getAll('http://localhost:5000');",
                  "    const jwt = cookies.find(c => c.key === 'jwt');",
                  "    pm.expect(jwt).to.exist;",
                  "    pm.expect(jwt.httpOnly).to.be.true;",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Rahul Kumar\",\n  \"email\": \"rahul.mentee@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePass123\",\n  \"role\": \"mentee\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/signup",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "signup"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
